{"tid":681533,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒評史上最佳：美斯第二 C.朗第三","createTime":"2018-05-28T06:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T11:27:03.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"77113b214c67ec1f57b599cdca433e77fd7d707e","tid":681533,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"巴爾在今季的歐冠盃決賽中表現出色，英國媒體當然不會放過這個吹捧自己人的機會，TV channel History公佈的史上最佳球員的排名中，巴爾已經殺進了前40，排名第35位。<br />\n<br />\n　　這份榜單中，排名榜首的是巴西球王比利，美斯和C.朗拿度分列第2和第3位。曼聯傳奇佐治-貝斯排名第4位。5-10位分別是馬勒當拿，波比-摩亞，告魯夫，波比-查爾頓，大衛碧咸和施丹。　　<br />\n<br />\n　　TV channel History這個歷史最佳評選的結果有不小的爭議，主要原因是英國球員的排名都很高，比如大衛碧咸的歷史排名甚至高過了施丹，說明英媒對自己人還是比較照顧的。<br />\n<br />\n　　TV channel History的副總裁丹-高漢在接受採訪時表示該評選創辦的意義就在於引發有趣的爭論，來評選史上最佳的球員和教練等。<br />\n<br />\n　　附：40人排名如下<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/05/28/d/d3fade0692258ee246a143d9d91dd89b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2Fd%2Fd3fade0692258ee246a143d9d91dd89b.jpg&h=b8d9582f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e058d390024fdf238d67453173af440a6fb8fe02","tid":681533,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"KDB已經入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8b82ffefe1ef7a39c26d0f31248bc5c9aa0ccf","tid":681533,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e058d390024fdf238d67453173af440a6fb8fe02","tid":681533,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"KDB已經入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"無RIVALDO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c89fcff5849fecf1485503fdb27995ca98c363e","tid":681533,"uid":41411,"like":52,"dislike":12,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"美斯&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;比利<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"52c6cd